var diachi_tt = window.opener.$(pDiachi_tt_name);
if(quan!=null) quan.value =$("quan").value;
/* Cap nhat dia chi lap hop dong ngay 24/11/2008 */
if(phuong!=null)
{ phuong.value =$("phuong").value;
if(phuong.value=='')
{ phuong.value=0;}
}
if(pho!=null)
{ pho.value =$("pho").value;
if( pho.value=='')
{ pho.value=0}
}
//if(phuong!=null) phuong.value =$("phuong").value;
//if(pho!=null) pho.value =$("pho").value;
if(sonha!=null) sonha.value =$("sonha").value;
if(diachi!=null) diachi.value =$("diachi").value;
if(diachi_tt!=null) diachi_tt.value =$("diachi").value;
if(quan==null||quan.value=='0'||phuong==null||phuong.value=='0'){
alert('Yeu cau chon Quan/Huyen va Phuong');
}else{
window.self.close();
}

function set_tinh_selected_index(){
if((pQuan_id.length<=0)){ //khong co gia tri tu caller truyen sang
loadQuan($("cboTinh"));
$("quan").focus();
return;
}
var obj = $('cboTmp');
if (obj==null) return;
var tmp;
for(var i=0;i<obj.length;i++) {
if (obj.options[i].value ==pQuan_id) {
tmp=obj.options[i].text;
break;
}
}
obj = $('cboTinh');
for(var i=0;i<obj.length;i++) {
if (obj.options[i].value ==tmp) {
obj.options[i].selected =true;
break;
}
}
loadQuan($("cboTinh"));
$("quan").focus();
}

class=textField onchange='load_phuong(this)' >"

+data
+"</SELECT>";

"<SELECT id=quan onkeydown=\"ChangeFromTabToEnter()\" style='width:98%'
class=textField onchange='load_phuong(this)'>"
+"<option value='0'></option>"
+"</SELECT>";
}
set_quan_selected_index();
load_phuong($('quan'));
}

//----------cap nhat du lieu theo cac su kien hoac callback cua ajax----
function capnhat_diachi(quan_id,phuong_id,pho_id,sonha_id,diachi_id) {
var sDiaChi="";
if ((firstLoad) && (pDiachi.length>1)) {// lan dau tien==> lay theo gia
tri truyen len
sDiaChi =Url.decode_1252(pDiachi);
firstLoad=false;
} else {
if (!isEmpty($(sonha_id).value)) sDiaChi+=$(sonha_id).value+" - ";
if
((!isEmpty($(pho_id).value))&&($(pho_id).value!="0")&&(trimBoth($("pho").
options[$("pho").selectedIndex].text)!=""))
sDiaChi+=$(pho_id).options[$(pho_id).selectedIndex].text+" - ";
if ((!isEmpty($(phuong_id).value))&&($(phuong_id).value!="0"))
sDiaChi+=$(phuong_id).options[$(phuong_id).selectedIndex].text+" - ";
if ((!isEmpty($(quan_id).value))&&($(quan_id).value!="0"))
sDiaChi+=$(quan_id).options[$(quan_id).selectedIndex].text+" - ";
if (!isEmpty($("cboTinh").value))
sDiaChi+=$("cboTinh").options[$("cboTinh").selectedIndex].text;
}
$(diachi_id).value=sDiaChi;
}
function focus_obj(v_obj) {
$(v_obj.id).focus();
}

if ((str=="") || (str.length==0)) return true;
}

alert(document.body.clientWidth +','+document.body.clientHeight)
}
function ChangeFromTabToEnter()
{
if(event.keyCode== 13)
event.keyCode = 9;
}

function dwrGetValue(data) {
if (data != null && typeof data == 'object') return
DWRUtil.toDescriptiveString(data, 2);
else return DWRUtil.toDescriptiveString(data, 1);
}
function dwrGetRecValueByFieldName(rec, fname)
{
for (var item in rec) {
if (item.toLowerCase() == fname.toLowerCase())
{
return Url.decode_1252(rec[item]);
}
}
return "";
}

function check_quyen_admin()
{

}
var reply_check_quyen=function(data)
{

{
$("chk_Edit").checked=false;
//$("chk_Edit").disabled=true;
}
else {
$("chk_Edit").disabled=false;
}
}

$("diachi").readOnly= false;

}

function cmdOK_click(){

return;
}

var pho= window.opener.$(pPho_id_name);
var sonha= window.opener.$(pSo_nha_name);
var diachi= window.opener.$(pDiachi_name);
var diachi_tt = window.opener.$(pDiachi_tt_name);
if(quan!=null) quan.value =$("quan").value;
/* Cap nhat dia chi lap hop dong ngay 24/11/2008 */
if(phuong!=null)
{ phuong.value =$("phuong").value;
if(phuong.value=='')
{ phuong.value=0;}
}
if(pho!=null)
{ pho.value =$("pho").value;
if( pho.value=='')
{ pho.value=0}
}
//if(phuong!=null) phuong.value =$("phuong").value;
//if(pho!=null) pho.value =$("pho").value;
if(sonha!=null) sonha.value =$("sonha").value;
if(diachi!=null) diachi.value =$("diachi").value;
if(diachi_tt!=null) diachi_tt.value =$("diachi").value;
if(quan==null||quan.value=='0'||phuong==null||phuong.value=='0'){
alert('Yeu cau chon Quan/Huyen va Phuong');
}else{
window.self.close();
}

function set_tinh_selected_index(){
if((pQuan_id.length<=0)){ //khong co gia tri tu caller truyen sang
loadQuan($("cboTinh"));
$("quan").focus();
return;
}
var obj = $('cboTmp');
if (obj==null) return;
var tmp;
for(var i=0;i<obj.length;i++) {
if (obj.options[i].value ==pQuan_id) {
tmp=obj.options[i].text;
break;
}
}
obj = $('cboTinh');
for(var i=0;i<obj.length;i++) {
if (obj.options[i].value ==tmp) {
obj.options[i].selected =true;
break;
}
}
loadQuan($("cboTinh"));
$("quan").focus();
}

function loadQuan(obj){
var psTinh=obj.options[obj.selectedIndex].value;
var url = 'neo.common.getUrlQuan("'+psTinh+'")';
DataRemoting.getDoc(url, cb_loadQuan);
}
var cb_loadQuan= function(data) {
if(!isEmpty(data)) {
$('ajaxQuan').innerHTML =
"<SELECT id=quan onkeydown=\"ChangeFromTabToEnter()\" style='width:98%'
class=textField onchange='load_phuong(this)' >"
+"<option value='0'>Không ch&#7885;n</option>"
+data
+"</SELECT>";
} else {
$('ajaxQuan').innerHTML =
"<SELECT id=quan onkeydown=\"ChangeFromTabToEnter()\" style='width:98%'
class=textField onchange='load_phuong(this)'>"
+"<option value='0'></option>"
+"</SELECT>";
}
set_quan_selected_index();
load_phuong($('quan'));
}

//----------cap nhat du lieu theo cac su kien hoac callback cua ajax----
function capnhat_diachi(quan_id,phuong_id,pho_id,sonha_id,diachi_id) {
var sDiaChi="";
if ((firstLoad) && (pDiachi.length>1)) {// lan dau tien==> lay theo gia
tri truyen len
sDiaChi =Url.decode_1252(pDiachi);
firstLoad=false;
} else {
if (!isEmpty($(sonha_id).value)) sDiaChi+=$(sonha_id).value+" - ";
if
((!isEmpty($(pho_id).value))&&($(pho_id).value!="0")&&(trimBoth($("pho").
options[$("pho").selectedIndex].text)!=""))
sDiaChi+=$(pho_id).options[$(pho_id).selectedIndex].text+" - ";
if ((!isEmpty($(phuong_id).value))&&($(phuong_id).value!="0"))
sDiaChi+=$(phuong_id).options[$(phuong_id).selectedIndex].text+" - ";
if ((!isEmpty($(quan_id).value))&&($(quan_id).value!="0"))
sDiaChi+=$(quan_id).options[$(quan_id).selectedIndex].text+" - ";
if (!isEmpty($("cboTinh").value))
sDiaChi+=$("cboTinh").options[$("cboTinh").selectedIndex].text;
}
$(diachi_id).value=sDiaChi;
}

$(v_obj.id).focus();
}

if ((str=="") || (str.length==0)) return true;
}

alert(document.body.clientWidth +','+document.body.clientHeight)
}
function ChangeFromTabToEnter()
{
if(event.keyCode== 13)
event.keyCode = 9;
}

function dwrGetValue(data) {
if (data != null && typeof data == 'object') return
DWRUtil.toDescriptiveString(data, 2);
else return DWRUtil.toDescriptiveString(data, 1);
}
function dwrGetRecValueByFieldName(rec, fname)
{
for (var item in rec) {
if (item.toLowerCase() == fname.toLowerCase())
{
return Url.decode_1252(rec[item]);
}
}
return "";
}
